data.description: Come see this absolute gem in a beautifully maintained gated community.  This very spacious split level home offers three bedrooms up and two on the lower level which creates two complete living spaces up and down.  Freshly updated with new lighting, a new deck and a brand new roof.  This maintenance free move in ready home is a perfect palette for you to make your dream home come to life. The backside of the home is fully fenced with a patio on the lower floor and that fresh new deck on the upper level.  A great place to enjoy those backyard soir'ees you've been dreaming about.  See this opportunity today before it passes you by.  With the holidays ahead you could be in by Christmas.
